</td>
<td style="width: 40%; text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b> <a href="/wiki/University_President" class="mw-redirect" title="University President">President</a> of <a href="/wiki/Yale_University" title="Yale University">Yale College</a> </b><br />1778–1795
</td>
